data.description: Charming home ready for you! Recent updates include Cooktop, Built in oven, A/C Unit, Roof, Bamboo Flooring, enclosed porch which is now the dining room 10 x 16', 4th bedroom is 9 x 7 for an additional 223 sf., interior paint & nice sized back yard w/endless possibilities. Great neighborhood w/easy walk to the pool or nearby coffee shop. Conveniently located near 281 & 410, just minutes from downtown San Antonio. Schedule your appointment today you will not be disappointed. Harmony Hills Cabana Club Optional for a fee(pool, club house, tennis & volleyball+)
